::EndBringer/Scyther/Demise/Incarcinator::

Demise reaches the mess hall, looking around to see if anyone's there.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The CR finishes, EndBringer ripping through the door instead of 
opening it. He hoped that Darkfate would't mind. He looks around 
briefly, bends the door back as well as he can, and then walks off 
toward the training rooms.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Scyther arrives at the bridge, looking around to see what was going 
on. He sees one of Crater's organic things slide by and frowns.0
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Incarcinator reaches the CR room, seeing the ripped-apart door. He 
sniffs, smelling EndBringer's scent.

"No wonder," he says to himself, entering a good CR and letting it 
repair him.
